Lost in Translation;;85;;95;;R;;A lonely, aging movie star named Bob Harris (Bill Murray) and a conflicted newlywed, Charlotte (Scarlett Johansson), meet in Tokyo. Bob is there to film a Japanese whiskey commercial; Charlotte is accompanying her celebrity-photographer husband. Strangers in a foreign land, the two find escape, distraction and understanding amidst the bright Tokyo lights after a chance meeting in the quiet lull of the hotel bar. They form a bond that is as unlikely as it is heartfelt and meaningful.;;Comedy,Drama;;Sofia Coppola;;2003;;Bill Murray,Scarlett Johansson,Giovanni Ribisi,Anna Faris,Fumihiro Hayashi,Catherine Lambert,Gregory Pekar,Richard Allen;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lost_in_translation